room_title: Escape room "Quarantine" by Extreme Escape Games in Nashville
review: Had a great time! Birthday party tonight for a 16-year-old, 4 family members and 5 friends. Lots of fun. Helpful and friendly staff. The setting of the zombie room was creepy. l definitely go try a different adventure at some point soon.

room_title: Escape room "Quarantine" by Extreme Escape Games in Nashville
review: I work at an escape room so I like to think I know when an escape room is awesome and their Quarantine room is AWESOME! Love the zombie element! Great live actor!

room_title: Escape room "Quarantine" by Extreme Escape Games in Nashville
review: Quarantine room. Dope. Actor. Stressful. Sweaty. Hard. Real good. Lots of interesting puzzles. Good props. Pumped.

room_title: Escape room "Quarantine" by Extreme Escape Games in Nashville
review: The Quarantine was so intense and fun!! So worth it and had a great 25th birthday for my son!

room_title: Escape room "Quarantine" by Extreme Escape Games in Nashville
review: This room was intense! Loved the character interaction. Perfect for the birthday party!
